The paper deals with computer vision and feature detection, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of virtual 3D environments and pre-selection of interest points also suggests a possible connection to graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves testing and analysis of performance, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
